      "status": "confirmed",
      "summary": "LOGSX is an earlier revision of the same GPS/LoRa tracker design (LOGSX v2). Same schematic structure with STM32F103, SX1273, TESEO-LIV3. Analyzer output is essentially identical to LOGSX v2 with the same correct detections and same errors.",
